HEADWORD: History
<hw>His"to*ry</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To narrate or record.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

